TEXT(beginproblem());


BEGIN_TEXT
$BR
Consider the series 
\[
    \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{(- $a)^{n-1}}{$b^n}
\]
Determine whether the series converges, and if it converges, determine its value.
$BR

Converges (y/n): \{ ans_rule()\}
$BR
Value if convergent (blank otherwise):  \{ans_rule(40)\}

$PAR
END_TEXT
    ANS(str_cmp("y"));
ANS(num_cmp( 1/($b + $a)  ));

